            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the<strong> stock</strong> to the pan with the chicken and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for a final 3 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Add the <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan and mix everything together until the spinach has slightly wilted – this is your <strong>fragrant chicken thigh & spinach broth</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
